1996-01-01|1996-12-30.description: Flex Mentallo relives his final battle against the Menace of the Mentallium Man and meets the deadly Killer Kitten, who provides an ominous clue toward finding his former comrade The Fact.
1996-01-01|1996-12-30.name: "After the Fact", Part Two: My Beautiful Head

1996-01-01|1996-12-30.description: How the Saint met his wife, and lost her; he goes back to Ratwater, looking for revenge and nearly gets it.
1996-01-01|1996-12-30.name: Saint of Killers Part 2

1996-01-01|1996-12-30.description: The Eternal Warrior takes the blind Geomancer, Clay McHenry, on a journey to enlightenment through the ritual of Chod. Together they'll face the spirit of a Geomancer long dead and defeat the twisted tulpa though-form that would claim the power of the line of Geomancers for itself forever.
1996-01-01|1996-12-30.name: Fist & Steel Pt. 2

1996-01-01|1996-12-30.description: Dimitri, the all-powerful echidna from history, has returned as Enerjak. Thrown aside by Enerjak into the desert, Knuckles has joined with the fire ant Archimedes, working together to stop him.
1996-01-01|1996-12-30.name: Rites of Passage - Part 2

1996-01-01|1996-12-30.description: The Death Egg duels with The Floating Island. This issue continues the Death Egg Saga as Sonic, Tails, and Knuckles and the Chaotix fight against the massive ship!
1996-01-01|1996-12-30.name: The Death Egg Saga, Part 2: Poached

volume.name: Sonic Quest: The Death Egg Saga

1996-01-01|1996-12-30.description: Lanyon and his boys are after Eddy. Eddy and Doogie are on the run trying to hide Uncle Charly, who used to be dead. Frank Arcko and Uncle Mitch are also looking for Eddy, but don't know that Charly is now a formerly dead guy. Confused? Don't ask Charly, he's just trying to get sober. Charly continues his story, complete with reflections and revelations. What really happened on the Brooklyn Bridge those years ago? This issue gives Charly's angle on what got his brother killed and made him go incognito. Will Arcko and Uncle Mitch find Eddy, Doogie and Uncle Charly before Lanyon can? And would that be a good thing for Charly?
1996-01-01|1996-12-30.name: Too Many Shots
